<section id="porto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sect-label reveal">Onde Tudo Começa</div>
    <div class="porto-grid">
      <div class="porto-text reveal reveal-d1">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:300;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.8rem);line-height:1.15;margin:16px 0 24px">Pântano do Sul</h2>
        <p>Saída de Pântano do Sul, no extremo sul da Ilha de Santa Catarina, Florianópolis/SC.</p>
        <p>Uma região rica em cultura açoriana, pesca artesanal e natureza preservada — o ponto de partida perfeito para explorar o que ainda é desconhecido.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="porto-map reveal reveal-d2">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 360 300" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;max-width:340px">
          <path d="M180 20C200 20 240 40 260 80C275 110 270 140 280 170C285 195 270 220 250 245C235 265 210 280 190 285C170 280 150 265 135 245C120 225 110 200 115 175C118 155 130 140 125 110C118 75 155 20 180 20Z" stroke="var(--blue-lt)" stroke-width="1.2" opacity=".5"></path>
          <circle cx="175" cy="250" r="5" fill="var(--gold-lt)"></circle>
          <text x="140" y="270" fill="var(--text)" font-family="var(--sans)" font-size="9" font-weight="400" letter-spacing="1">Pântano do Sul</text>
          <circle cx="195" cy="278" r="3" fill="var(--blue-lt)"></circle>
          <text x="208" y="282" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="var(--sans)" font-size="8" letter-spacing=".5">Naufragados</text>
          <circle cx="230" cy="255" r="3" fill="var(--blue-lt)"></circle>
          <text x="240" y="259" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="var(--sans)" font-size="8" letter-spacing=".5">Três Irmãs</text>
          <circle cx="220" cy="295" r="3" fill="var(--blue-lt)"></circle>
          <circle cx="228" cy="292" r="2" fill="var(--blue-lt)"></circle>
          <text x="140" y="298" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="var(--sans)" font-size="8" letter-spacing=".5">Moleques do Sul</text>
          <circle cx="150" cy="235" r="3" fill="var(--blue-lt)"></circle>
          <text x="85" y="232" fill="var(--text-dim)" font-family="var(--sans)" font-size="8" letter-spacing=".5">Lagoinha do Leste</text>
          <text x="180" y="48" fill="var(--text-faint)" font-family="var(--sans)" font-size="8" letter-spacing="2" text-anchor="middle">SUL DA ILHA</text>
          <line x1="175" y1="250" x2="220" y2="295" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width=".6" stroke-dasharray="4 4" opacity=".4"></line>
          <line x1="175" y1="250" x2="230" y2="255" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width=".6" stroke-dasharray="4 4" opacity=".4"></line>
          <line x1="175" y1="250" x2="195" y2="278" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width=".6" stroke-dasharray="4 4" opacity=".4"></line>
        </svg>
